item.title: Woodcutting
item.dc:creator: @pk4pk pk4pk
item.description:
@pk4pk wrote:

[quote=“cooper, post:18, topic:196569”][quote author=pk4pk link=topic=261177.msg2175538#msg2175538 date=1207803005]

I am level 81, I cut yews from 60-81. I just switched to dragon axe at Barbarian Assault willows and I have never seen woodcutting this fast. Much faster than maples.

You must tell me this ‘barbarian assault’ you speak of…is it packed like at draynor? Is it close to a bank? Should I buy a Dragon axe at 60? (3 levels left) Do dragon axes speed anything up actually?
[/quote]
Rarely packed, if it is, many many many many many worlds are available. Close to a bank deposit box, a little bit farther to a bank. And I wouldn’t really recommend it at 60, but you can if you can spare the money, and yes they do speed you up quite a bit.[/quote]
I was looking at the world map and I didn’t find a bank at barbarian assault
